{"tid":1430533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再同人爭論laser有冇殺傷力啦","createTime":"2019-08-07T18:31:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T19:46:56.000Z","uid":89419,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3e19ff0f4c0d105c822cc71a2581c98d4db78992","tid":1430533,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:31:38.000Z","msg":"菜刀界刀生果刀萬用刀夠有殺傷力啦<br />\n火機火柴消毒火酒人頭馬夠有殺傷力啦<br />\n雞蛋蕃茄水樽遮基本上所有物件都有殺傷力<br />\n我嬲起上黎用條底褲都殺得死你<br />\n係咪買所有野都要有機會比你拉呀<br />\n佢個記者會個所謂實驗就同攞把生果刀出黎同你講佢切得開個橙一樣 跟本就冇黎啦肺<br />\n宜家個問題係佢都未去用呢樣野你就話個人有機會用呢樣野去犯法<br />\n仲勁過未審先判<br />\n佢根本唔志在告得入睇佢證物都照攞出黎玩就知<br />\n啲狗用一個錯漏百出嘅實驗仔就成功轉移曬大部份人嘅焦點<br />\n只要佢地每日出黎做埸大龍鳳<br />\n好快香港人就再冇人記得五大訴求<br />\n手足們 啲狗係好笑 不過我地記住要集中焦點<br />\n唔好咁易比人玩到氹氹轉呀<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e3e160243b449b490cbd5c8d61052c7b162ff936","tid":1430533,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:32:29.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"5a45347a511cf9d7d75f40f80ea2f1214275d5d9","tid":1430533,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:32:51.000Z","msg":"2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7768970829fc25ca03f2fa1e7306dc5dc75519","tid":1430533,"uid":209337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:32:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4d7e26dbae3fa25d536ec1fe4e6a6ea583f69dda","tid":1430533,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:33:11.000Z","msg":"3<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f9bc3dc7821677a5a60a2462e34f0c630c462f","tid":1430533,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:33:31.000Z","msg":"4<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e24d3a931fca1eeba683e233daa3ece18d85cda","tid":1430533,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor