:41:33.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n而家唔係支筆可唔可以傷人嘅問題<br />\n而係佢未攻擊 警方就濫捕嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n可以睇下黃國桐律師嘅解說<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/2717416301699742?s=1170485742&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F2717416301699742%3Fs%3D1170485742%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=568e9f84\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/2717416301699742?s=1170485742&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"4d28fc727b0dd1271d74b35c94727f0621ccc9d3","tid":1430533,"uid":89419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aa525a365582870f3b84779f16991f52cb958791","tid":1430533,"uid":107097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:34:04.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n個重點係無證據用來攻擊點解可以拉人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:43:45.000Z","msg":"比佢證明左可以用黎攻擊咁又點<br />\n比我地證明左唔可以用黎攻擊咁又點<br />\n<br />\n個重點係 <br />\n你都證明唔到我將會用枝筆黎作攻擊 <br />\n你淨係話好多人用枝筆黎作攻擊<br />\n所以你就估我會用枝筆黎攻擊人<br />\n<br />\n例子:刀仔<br />\n只要曾經有人用刀仔吉傷一個人<br />\n啲狗就可以估你買刀仔就係用黎吉人<br />\n<br />\n例子:條撚<br />\n只要警黑揾幾個人出黎周圍老強下<br />\n佢就可以因為你帶左一條勃起嘅撚出街而拉你"},{"pid":"4a24aa75cf909e613190f43d4b9ffe8fb3016b44","tid":1430533,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:45:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6874096d59095a7cf82673eae55a3f4775e79945","tid":1430533,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:47:18.000Z","msg":"只可以話黑警今次個局set得唔錯<br />\n好多把持唔住嘅市民已經中左氹"},{"pid":"e4bf5155ec0cda6921f6795a32df5c003f0a58c8","tid":1430533,"uid":275074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T18:50:15.000Z","msg":"必順做多啲文宣"},{"pid":"15d0177c34c3ea8744dc7a4b1d8932d8f15b72fc","tid":1430533,"uid":89419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T19:43:56.000Z","msg":"訓前一推<br />\n希望聽日起身見到大家都輕鬆完<br />\n焦點對翻準濫捕問題<br />\n繼續堅持五大訴求"},{"pid":"5d25c86ddc06d8df917ce